  <!-- EN: Progressive mending -->
  <Mending_progressiveMending>渐进式修补</Mending_progressiveMending>
  <!-- EN: The level of repairing an item depends on the skill of the pawn responsible for performing the repair (by default, Crafting). \n\nEach new pawn skill level increases the repair limit by 5%. 100% repair corresponds to level 20 pawn skill. \n\nThe amount of the bonus is added to the pawn's skill level, but the resulting repair level cannot exceed 100%. -->
  <Mending_progressiveMending_Tooltip>修复物品的等级取决于工作人员的技能等级（默认情况下为手工技能）。\n\n工作人员的每提高一级技能，对应的修复上限提高5%。20级手工技能对应100%修复上限。\n\n提高技能能够增加修复上限，但是最终不能超过100%。</Mending_progressiveMending_Tooltip>

  <!-- EN: Repair skill bonus: (+{0}) -->
  <Mending_pawnFreeSkillBonus_Label>技能奖励：（+{0}）</Mending_pawnFreeSkillBonus_Label>
  <!-- EN: The number of bonus points for the pawn repair skill. Allows you to reach the maximum repair level earlier. -->
  <Mending_pawnFreeSkillBonus_ToolTip>人员修理技能加成点数。能够让你更早达到100%极限的维修水平。</Mending_pawnFreeSkillBonus_ToolTip>

  <!-- EN: Reduce the quality of an item on error -->
  <Mending_decreaseQualityOnFail>修补失败时降低物品品质</Mending_decreaseQualityOnFail>
  <!-- EN: Failure during Mending cause decreasing the quality of the item by 1 step. -->
  <Mending_decreaseQualityOnFail_Tooltip>在修补过程中失败，将导致物品的质量下降1级。</Mending_decreaseQualityOnFail_Tooltip>

